data.title: Chłopi. Wydanie kolekcjonerskie - Reymont Władysław Stanisław - POLSKA...
data.meta_description: An exclusive edition of the Nobel Prize-winning work by Władysław Stanisław Reymont. The film was based on paintings from the Young Poland period, which perfectly capture the mood of Reymont's prose.
